# RQ-53-10-01-181: Impact Detection System

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall detect and log bird strike, hail, or other impact events with timestamp and g-level data.

## Rationale
Automated impact detection triggers maintenance inspection.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Impact threshold: 10g acceleration (3Ïƒ above flight loads)
- Event logging with timestamp
- Automatic alert generation
- Data retention for 5 years

## Compliance Status
System design complete, testing planned
